{"tid":797013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭巴士俾人偷拍","createTime":"2018-08-28T07:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T08:18:09.000Z","uid":202834,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f97c3131f65f5d33a06102d7cfd8fb9a45af7d","tid":797013,"uid":202834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"平時偷拍新聞就聽得多，估唔到今日真係會發身係我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果怕太長，可以直接碌落最低睇簡短版<br />\n<br />\n先講咗我今日既衣著：普通白色t-shirt，藍色長褲，白布鞋，長頭髮，樣唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">一陣又俾連登仔話我著到成隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁，抵俾人影</span></span><br />\n<br />\n說話今日朝早返工，搭巴士過海<br />\n一上到車，緊係第一時間去上層搵位坐<br />\n晨早流流起身返工，搭車就順便補眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正過海巴士有排搭<br />\n瞓瞓下感覺到隔離位條友隻手係咁&quot;hi&quot;我個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擘大眼睇下，見到隔離位個肥佬（30歲左右）都瞓緊覺<br />\n心諗佢應該唔係有心抽水，人地朝起身返工都會攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 架車又浪下浪下，掂到隔離位好平常，應該冇心<br />\n咁我合返埋眼繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓多唔夠十分鐘，我醒咗<br />\n<br />\n一擘大眼，眼尾望下隔離個肥佬做緊咩<br />\n屌，佢開部手機個自拍鏡頭影緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時我已經擘大眼，佢影咗幾張<br />\n佢發現我醒咗，即刻收埋手機扮冇野<br />\n我問佢：你做咩影我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n肥佬：冇野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個下好撚嬲，落咗去下層企都唔想同佢坐<br />\n結果我冇向司機投訴，冇報狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利申：我係巴打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係，我係男人，不過留長頭髮<br />\n<br />\n一定有人問我點解唔搞大件事：<br />\n我係男人，就算我大嗌偷拍都唔會有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非我係女人<br />\n又冇證據，就算我搶佢手機，佢唔肯解鎖佢部手機都冇用<br />\n<br />\n點解唔向司機投訴/報狗<br />\n向司機投訴，司機一定叫我報狗<br />\n一報狗即係要成架車既人陪我等狗到<br />\n返工時段做呢樣野，一定俾成車人屌到反皮，實會話「男人怕咩俾人影」「邊有人得閒偷拍男人」<br />\n<br />\n諗返起真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個肥佬偷拍我都唔知有咩意途<br />\n如果係gay佬更加嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心gay佬就死埋一二邊啦，我唔反對人搞gay，但係你地咪撚搞其他男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係所有男人都係gay<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打小心啲，依家香港好撚多gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡短版：<br />\n今日我搭巴士俾隔離個肥佬偷拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我係巴打<br />\n<br />\n以上絕對真人真事，如果我講大話、吹水，爛春袋、死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bf5793639a1f06574a4587d24bc6f007012dc9","tid":797013,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4388a15889ef61cfffbb918848fc60d852acdf25","tid":797013,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"THIS"},{"pid":"75a8899279f11084b697fc8a8f83965e82018caa","tid":797013,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"自貼睇吓點嘅樣先"},{"pid":"17c19216be50c6bb294dc46f1ca50732d11b637d","tid":797013,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"男人老狗都唔報驚<br />\n咁有乜撚好講"},{"pid":"a9bc29331f7b1e7bcc917b72bb1640eae798ccfe","tid":797013,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"男女平等呢？"},{"pid":"765067526fafae184f3b23245612da75dce218ff","tid":797013,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadb48fd52a38f7e3f9c13db2441a33d11157b38","tid":797013,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"Great"},{"pid":"6a61f32b4aebdf9aad3346ca008acc89f7e202cf","tid":797013,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}